🛰️ Space Fact of the Day

Hyperspectral satellites capture hundreds of narrow spectral bands, unlike normal RGB imaging.

They enable detection of:

* 🌱 Crop & soil health
* 🪨 Mineral deposits
* 🏭 Pollution levels
* 💧 Water contamination

📌 *Hyperspectral imaging = micro-level insights that transform Earth observation.*

