🧠 Embedded Concept of the Day

# OBC – On-Board Computer

The OBC is the **central brain of a satellite**, responsible for:

* 📡 Sensor data acquisition
* 🔁 Telemetry & telecommands
* 🔌 Power distribution
* ⏱ Real-time scheduling (RTOS)
* 🛡 Fault-tolerant operations

💡 *Runs on:* **RTOS**, **Bare-metal C**, **radiation-hardened processors**

